---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "Privacy Policy — MatchDayLive";
const description = "How Matchday Media collects, uses and protects your personal data when you use MatchDayLive.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} noindex={true}>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-linear-to-b from-charcoal-pitch to-navy-umpire px-6 pb-20 pt-40">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-200 text-center text-white">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-[50px] font-medium uppercase leading-[0.9] tracking-[-1px] md:text-[72px]">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-100 font-body text-[16px] leading-[1.5] text-white/70">
        Last updated: April 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="bg-white px-6 py-20 md:py-30">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-160 space-y-10 font-body text-[16px] leading-[1.7] text-text-primary">

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-[28px] font-medium uppercase leading-[0.9] tracking-[-1px] text-charcoal-pitch">1. Who We Are</h2>
        <p>MatchDayLive is operated by Matchday Media, a company registered in the United Kingdom. We are the data controller for personal data collected through <strong>matchdaylive.com</strong>.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">For data enquiries, contact us at: <a href="mailto:privacy@matchdaylive.com" class="text-text-action underline">privacy@matchdaylive.com</a></p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-[28px] font-medium uppercase leading-[0.9] tracking-[-1px] text-charcoal-pitch">2. Data We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you use MatchDayLive or enquire about our platform, we may collect:</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
          <li>Contact information (name, email address, organisation name)</li>
          <li>Account credentials for the MatchDayLive management platform</li>
          <li>Payment information — processed exclusively by Stripe (we do not store card data)</li>
          <li>Usage data and analytics (page views, feature usage, session data)</li>
          <li>Video playback metrics (via Bitmovin analytics)</li>
          <li>Support conversation history (via Intercom)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-[28px] font-medium uppercase leading-[0.9] tracking-[-1px] text-charcoal-pitch">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
          <li>To provide and operate the MatchDayLive platform</li>
          <li>To process payments and manage billing</li>
          <li>To provide customer support</li>
          <li>To send product updates and relevant communications (with your consent)</li>
          <li>To improve our platform through analytics</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-[28px] font-medium uppercase leading-[0.9] tracking-[-1px] text-charcoal-pitch">4. Third-Party Processors</h2>
        <p>We use the following trusted third-party services to operate our platform:</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
          <li><strong>Stripe</strong> — payment processing (PCI DSS Level 1 certified)</li>
          <li><strong>Amazon Web Services (CloudFront, S3, Lambda)</strong> — content delivery and infrastructure</li>
          <li><strong>Intercom</strong> — customer support chat</li>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> — website analytics</li>
          <li><strong>Bitmovin</strong> — video player and playback analytics</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">Each provider is bound by appropriate data processing agreements.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-[28px] font-medium uppercase leading-[0.9] tracking-[-1px] text-charcoal-pitch">5. Your Rights (UK GDPR)</h2>
        <p>Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request erasure of your data</li>
          <li>Object to or restrict processing</li>
          <li>Data portability</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time (where processing is based on consent)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">To exercise any of these rights, contact <a href="mailto:privacy@matchdaylive.com" class="text-text-action underline">privacy@matchdaylive.com</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-[28px] font-medium uppercase leading-[0.9] tracking-[-1px] text-charcoal-pitch">6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain personal data for as long as necessary to provide our services and comply with legal obligations. Account data is deleted within 90 days of account closure upon request.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-[28px] font-medium uppercase leading-[0.9] tracking-[-1px] text-charcoal-pitch">7. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any privacy-related queries or to exercise your rights:</p>
        <p class="mt-2"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@matchdaylive.com" class="text-text-action underline">privacy@matchdaylive.com</a></p>
        <p class="mt-1">You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the <a href="https://ico.org.uk" class="text-text-action underline" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Information Commissioner's Office (ICO)</a>.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
